# Tools++ scripts — no Beta APIs

Tools++ behavior-pack scripts (`@minecraft/server` 2.7.0) work on normal worlds with the pack activated. **Do not instruct the user to enable Beta APIs** for XP rewards, furnace smelt tracking, or digger tool durability.

World experiments that *are* sometimes needed (unrelated to scripts):

- **Creation of Custom Biomes** — ruby ore world generation only
- **Upcoming Creator Features** — optional 3D block item icons (see minecraft-bedrock-blocks skill)

For script details, read `.cursor/skills/minecraft-bedrock-scripts/SKILL.md`.
